      <title>Hexo-Yilia主题配置</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/18/hexo-yilia-zhu-ti-pei-zhi/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/18/hexo-yilia-zhu-ti-pei-zhi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>-</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Hexo-Yilia主题配置"><a href="#Hexo-Yilia主题配置" class="headerlink" title="Hexo-Yilia主题配置"></a>Hexo-Yilia主题配置</h2><p>Yilia主题网址:<a href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git">https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git</a></p><h4 id="设置基本信息"><a href="#设置基本信息" class="headerlink" title="设置基本信息"></a>设置基本信息</h4><ul><li>头像<ul><li>avatar: 头像图片路径</li><li>favicon: 网站图标路径</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="“所有文章”功能配置"><a href="#“所有文章”功能配置" class="headerlink" title="“所有文章”功能配置"></a>“所有文章”功能配置</h4><ul><li><p>在blog根目录中执行如下命令:</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$npm</span> i hexo-generator-json-content --save</code></pre></li><li><p>在blog根目录中_config.yml配置文件中添加如下配置</p><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml">jsonContent:    meta: false    pages: false    posts:    title: true    date: true    path: true    text: false    raw: false    content: false    slug: false    updated: false    comments: false    link: false    permalink: false    excerpt: false    categories: false    tags: true</code></pre></li></ul><h4 id="配置个人链接图片"><a href="#配置个人链接图片" class="headerlink" title="配置个人链接图片"></a>配置个人链接图片</h4><ul><li><p>在/themes/yilia/source/中新建assets目录，并添加链接图片</p></li><li><p>在/themes/yilia/_config.yml配置文件中</p><ul><li><p>在subnav中配置个人链接路径</p><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml">subnav:  #github: "#"  #weibo: "#"  #rss: "#"  #zhihu: "#"  qq: "/assets/QQ.jpg"  weixin: "/assets/WeChat.jpg"  #jianshu: "#"  #douban: "#"  #segmentfault: "#"  #bilibili: "#"  #acfun: "#"  mail: "mailto:824491225@qq.com"  #facebook: "#"  #google: "#"  #twitter: "#"  #linkedin: "#"</code></pre></li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="配置打赏"><a href="#配置打赏" class="headerlink" title="配置打赏"></a>配置打赏</h4><ul><li>在/themes/yilia/_config.yml配置文件中<ul><li>reward_type<ul><li>0 关闭打赏</li><li>1 reward:true属性的文章才有打赏</li><li>2 所有文章均有打赏</li></ul></li><li>reward_woding: 打赏提示语</li><li>alipay: 支付宝支付图片路径</li><li>weixin: 微信支付图片路径</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="左侧显示总文章数"><a href="#左侧显示总文章数" class="headerlink" title="左侧显示总文章数"></a>左侧显示总文章数</h4><p>在/themes/yilia/layout/_partial/left-col.ejs文件中，<nav class="header-menu">标签后添加</nav></p><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><nav>    总文章数 <%=site.posts.length%></nav></code></pre><h4 id="显示文章摘要"><a href="#显示文章摘要" class="headerlink" title="显示文章摘要"></a>显示文章摘要</h4><p>在md格式的文章中添加<!-- more -->  标签后面的内容不显示</p><h4 id="文章显示目录"><a href="#文章显示目录" class="headerlink" title="文章显示目录"></a>文章显示目录</h4><p>在themes/yilia/_config.yml中设置toc为2</p><h4 id="添加归档"><a href="#添加归档" class="headerlink" title="添加归档"></a>添加归档</h4><p>在themes/yilia/_config.yml中设置menu</p><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml">menu:  归档: /archives/index.html</code></pre><h4 id="文章插入网易云音乐"><a href="#文章插入网易云音乐" class="headerlink" title="文章插入网易云音乐"></a>文章插入网易云音乐</h4><ul><li>获取音乐HTML代码</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-yilia-zhu-ti-pei-zhi/image-20200818145954925.png" alt="image-20200818145954925"></p><ul><li>md格式文章中添加HTML代码</li></ul><h4 id="博客插入背景音乐"><a href="#博客插入背景音乐" class="headerlink" title="博客插入背景音乐"></a>博客插入背景音乐</h4><ul><li>获取音乐HTML代码</li></ul><p>![image-20200818145954925](../../../Typora workplace/other/Hexo-Yilia主题配置/image-20200818145954925.png)</p><ul><li><p>在themes/yilia/layout/_partial/left-col.ejs文件中nav标签中添加如下代码:</p><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><% if (theme.music && theme.music.enable)&#123; %>    <div style="position:absolute; bottom:120px left:auto; width:85%">        音乐HTML代码    </div><% &#125; %></code></pre></li><li><p>在themes/yilia/_config.yml中配置</p><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml"># 网易云音乐插件music:  enable: true # 是否开启音乐功能  autoplay: true  # 是否开启自动播放</code></pre></li></ul><h4 id="“微信分享”功能配置"><a href="#“微信分享”功能配置" class="headerlink" title="“微信分享”功能配置"></a>“微信分享”功能配置</h4><p>在themes/yilia/layout/_partial/post/share.ejs文件中</p><p>在</p><pre><code>var sUrl = url.replace(/index\.html$/, &#39;&#39;);sUrl = /^(http:|https:)\/\//.test(sUrl) ? sUrl : &#39;http:&#39; + sUrl;</code></pre><p>后面添加</p><pre><code>test=sUrl.substring(20);</code></pre><p>将</p><pre><code>//pan.baidu.com/share/qrcode?url=&#39; + sUrl</code></pre><p>改为</p><pre><code>//api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&amp;data=主页网址&#39; + test</code></pre><h4 id="文章置顶"><a href="#文章置顶" class="headerlink" title="文章置顶"></a>文章置顶</h4><ul><li>安装插件</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$npm</span> uninstall hexo-generator-index --save<span class="token variable">$npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-generator-index-pin-top --save</code></pre><ul><li>在/themes/主题/layout/post.ejs中,最前面添加如下代码</li></ul><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><% if (page.top) &#123; %>  <i class="fa fa-thumb-tack"></i>  <font color=7D26CD>置顶</font>  <span class="post-meta-divider">|</span><% &#125; %></code></pre><ul><li>在文章的Front-matter中添加top: 值，值越大，优先级越高</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token hr punctuation">---</span>title: 2019date: 2019-02-14 16:10:03<span class="token title important">top: 5<span class="token punctuation">---</span></span></code></pre><ul><li><p>在blog根目录_config.yml配置文件中</p><ul><li>top</li><li>date</li></ul><p>属性值</p><ul><li>1 正序</li><li>-1 倒序</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="文章加密"><a href="#文章加密" class="headerlink" title="文章加密"></a>文章加密</h4><ul><li>安装插件</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-blog-encrypt</code></pre><ul><li>在blog根目录_config.yml配置文件中设置</li></ul><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml">encrypt:    enable: true</code></pre><ul><li>在文章的Front-matter中<ul><li>password: 密码</li><li>abstract: 博客显示的摘要信息</li><li>message: 输入密码的提示信息</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="鼠标点击小红心"><a href="#鼠标点击小红心" class="headerlink" title="鼠标点击小红心"></a>鼠标点击小红心</h4><ul><li>在/themes/yilia/source中新建love.js文件</li></ul><pre class=" language-JS"><code class="language-JS">!function(e,t,a)&#123;function r()&#123;for(var e=0;e<s.length;e++)s[e].alpha<=0?(t.body.removeChild(s[e].el),s.splice(e,1)):(s[e].y--,s[e].scale+=.004,s[e].alpha-=.013,s[e].el.style.cssText="left:"+s[e].x+"px;top:"+s[e].y+"px;opacity:"+s[e].alpha+";transform:scale("+s[e].scale+","+s[e].scale+") rotate(45deg);background:"+s[e].color+";z-index:99999");requestAnimationFrame(r)&#125;function n()&#123;var t="function"==typeof e.onclick&&e.onclick;e.onclick=function(e)&#123;t&&t(),o(e)&#125;&#125;function o(e)&#123;var a=t.createElement("div");a.className="heart",s.push(&#123;el:a,x:e.clientX-5,y:e.clientY-5,scale:1,alpha:1,color:c()&#125;),t.body.appendChild(a)&#125;function i(e)&#123;var a=t.createElement("style");a.type="text/css";try&#123;a.appendChild(t.createTextNode(e))&#125;catch(t)&#123;a.styleSheet.cssText=e&#125;t.getElementsByTagName("head")[0].appendChild(a)&#125;function c()&#123;return"rgb("+~~(255*Math.random())+","+~~(255*Math.random())+","+~~(255*Math.random())+")"&#125;var s=[];e.requestAnimationFrame=e.requestAnimationFrame||e.webkitRequestAnimationFrame||e.mozRequestAnimationFrame||e.oRequestAnimationFrame||e.msRequestAnimationFrame||function(e)&#123;setTimeout(e,1e3/60)&#125;,i(".heart&#123;width: 10px;height: 10px;position: fixed;background: #f00;transform: rotate(45deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(45deg);-moz-transform: rotate(45deg);&#125;.heart:after,.heart:before&#123;content: '';width: inherit;height: inherit;background: inherit;border-radius: 50%;-webkit-border-radius: 50%;-moz-border-radius: 50%;position: fixed;&#125;.heart:after&#123;top: -5px;&#125;.heart:before&#123;left: -5px;&#125;"),n(),r()&#125;(window,document);</code></pre><ul><li>在/themes/yilia/layout/_partial/footer.ejs文件中最后添加</li></ul><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><script type="text/javascript" src="/love.js"></script></code></pre><h4 id="不蒜子统计"><a href="#不蒜子统计" class="headerlink" title="不蒜子统计"></a>不蒜子统计</h4><h5 id="安装不蒜子脚本"><a href="#安装不蒜子脚本" class="headerlink" title="安装不蒜子脚本"></a>安装不蒜子脚本</h5><p>在themes/yilia/layout/_partial/after-footer.ejs文件中最后添加</p><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><script  async  src="https://dn-lbstatics.qbox.me/busuanzi/2.3/busuanzi.pure.mini.js"></script></code></pre><h5 id="单篇文章点击量"><a href="#单篇文章点击量" class="headerlink" title="单篇文章点击量"></a>单篇文章点击量</h5><p>在themes/yilia/layout/_partial/article.ejs文件中，在</p><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><%- partial('post/title', &#123;class_name: 'article-title'&#125;) %></code></pre><p>后面添加</p><pre class=" language-ejs"><code class="language-ejs"><!--显示阅读次数--><% if (!index && post.comments)&#123; %>  <br/>  <a class="cloud-tie-join-count" href="javascript:void(0);" style="color:gray;font-size:14px;">  <span class="icon-sort"></span>  <span id="busuanzi_container_page_pv" style="color:#ef7522;font-size:14px;">            阅读数: <span id="busuanzi_value_page_pv"></span>次 &nbsp;&nbsp;  </span>  </a><% &#125; %><!--显示阅读次数完毕--></code></pre><h4 id="404页面"><a href="#404页面" class="headerlink" title="404页面"></a>404页面</h4><p>​        直接在hexo/source文件夹里面加一个404.html.</p><h4 id="参考文档"><a href="#参考文档" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h4><p><a href="http://dongshuyan.com/2019/05/24/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9/">http://dongshuyan.com/2019/05/24/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9/</a></p><p><a href="https://cloudy-liu.github.io/2018/04/07/Hexo_yilia_%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%80%E6%8F%BD%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/">https://cloudy-liu.github.io/2018/04/07/Hexo_yilia_%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%80%E6%8F%BD%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</a></p><p><a href="https://joeybling.github.io/ibooks/hexo/hexo_music.html">https://joeybling.github.io/ibooks/hexo/hexo_music.html</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
