      <title>Hexo-搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>-</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="一-下载与安装Git"><a href="#一-下载与安装Git" class="headerlink" title="一. 下载与安装Git"></a>一. 下载与安装Git</h3><h4 id="1-下载"><a href="#1-下载" class="headerlink" title="1.下载"></a>1.下载</h4><p>​        Git官网网址为: <a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com</a></p><p>点击Downloads</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818074822924.png" alt="image-20200818074822924"></p><p>选择Windows版本</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818074916174.png" alt="image-20200818074916174"></p><p>选择64位版本</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818075734543.png" alt="image-20200818075734543"></p><h4 id="2-安装"><a href="#2-安装" class="headerlink" title="2.安装"></a>2.安装</h4><p>​        一直点击Next即可.</p><h4 id="3-配置"><a href="#3-配置" class="headerlink" title="3.配置"></a>3.配置</h4><h5 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h5><ul><li>配置Git用户名与邮箱</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">git</span>  config --global  user.name  <span class="token string">'GitHub用户名'</span><span class="token function">git</span>  config --global  user.email  <span class="token string">'GitHub邮箱'</span></code></pre><h6 id="参考文档"><a href="#参考文档" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h6><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/ximiaomiao/p/7140456.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/ximiaomiao/p/7140456.html</a></p><h5 id="生成SSH-Key并连接GitHub"><a href="#生成SSH-Key并连接GitHub" class="headerlink" title="生成SSH Key并连接GitHub"></a>生成SSH Key并连接GitHub</h5><p>在 Git Bash中执行以下命令</p><ul><li>查看是否存在SSH key</li></ul><p>​       检查本机用户home目录中是否存在SSH Key，如果存在则跳到第三步</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$cd</span> ~/.ssh</code></pre><ul><li>创建SSH Key</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$ssh</span>-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="token string">"GitHub邮箱"</span></code></pre><p>​            提示输入SSH Key文件存储路径，直接回车（选择默认路径）</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">Generating public/private rsa key pair.Enter <span class="token function">file</span> <span class="token keyword">in</span> <span class="token function">which</span> to save the key <span class="token punctuation">(</span>/c/Users/Lenovo/.ssh/id_rsa<span class="token punctuation">)</span>:</code></pre><p>​            提示输入密码，直接回车（空密码）</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">Enter passphrase <span class="token punctuation">(</span>empty <span class="token keyword">for</span> no passphrase<span class="token punctuation">)</span>:</code></pre><p>​            提示确认密码，直接回车</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">Enter same passphrase again:</code></pre><p>​            提示密码生成信息</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">Your identification has been saved <span class="token keyword">in</span> /c/Users/Lenovo/.ssh/id_rsaYour public key has been saved <span class="token keyword">in</span> /c/Users/Lenovo/.ssh/id_rsa.pubThe key fingerprint is:SHA256:/MJjjpNCdfM/MAafADt/gxqDMLewnrdOEi0MoVviUj4 824491225@qq.comThe key's randomart image is:+---<span class="token punctuation">[</span>RSA 3072<span class="token punctuation">]</span>----+<span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token keyword">.</span>                <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token punctuation">..</span>    <span class="token keyword">.</span>          <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span>+ o    o         <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span>.O+<span class="token punctuation">..</span> +.<span class="token operator">=</span>        <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span>o.E*.+ +SB <span class="token keyword">.</span>     <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token keyword">.</span> .++ o.o.X      <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token punctuation">..</span>o.  <span class="token operator">==</span>o.<span class="token operator">=</span>     <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span>  ooo ++ o  o    <span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token operator">|</span>   ooo<span class="token punctuation">..</span>.    <span class="token keyword">.</span>   <span class="token operator">|</span>+----<span class="token punctuation">[</span>SHA256<span class="token punctuation">]</span>-----+</code></pre><ul><li><p>在GitHub添加SSH Key</p><ul><li><p>拷贝SSH Key</p><p>在Git Bash中执行命令:</p></li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$clip</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</code></pre><ul><li><p>设置GitHub的SSH Key</p><ul><li>选择Settings</li></ul><h6 id><a href="#" class="headerlink" title></a><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818083941997.png" alt="image-20200818083941997"></h6><ul><li>选择SSH and GPG keys，点击New SSH Key</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818084203191.png" alt="image-20200818084203191"></p><ul><li>在Key中粘贴SSH Key，并点击Add SSH Key</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818084419732.png" alt="image-20200818084419732"></p></li></ul></li><li><p>测试SSH Key</p><p>在Git Bash中执行命令</p></li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$ssh</span> -T git@github.com</code></pre><p>​        提示信息1:</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">The authenticity of host <span class="token string">'github.com (207.97.227.239)'</span> can't be established.RSA key fingerprint is 16:27:ac:a5:76:28:2d:36:63:1b:56:4d:eb:df:a6:48.Are you sure you want to <span class="token keyword">continue</span> connecting <span class="token punctuation">(</span>yes/no<span class="token punctuation">)</span>?</code></pre><p>​            输入yes，提示</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">Hi username<span class="token operator">!</span> You＇ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</code></pre><p>​        提示信息2:</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">Hi username<span class="token operator">!</span> You＇ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</code></pre><h6 id="参考文档-1"><a href="#参考文档-1" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h6><p><a href="https://www.xuanfengge.com/using-ssh-key-link-github-photo-tour.html">https://www.xuanfengge.com/using-ssh-key-link-github-photo-tour.html</a></p><h3 id="二-下载与安装Node-js"><a href="#二-下载与安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="二. 下载与安装Node.js"></a>二. 下载与安装Node.js</h3><h4 id="1-下载-1"><a href="#1-下载-1" class="headerlink" title="1.下载"></a>1.下载</h4><p>​        Node.js官网网址为:<a href="https://nodejs.org/">https://nodejs.org</a></p><p>选择LTS版本</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818090345443.png" alt="image-20200818090345443"></p><h4 id="2-安装-1"><a href="#2-安装-1" class="headerlink" title="2.安装"></a>2.安装</h4><p>​        一直点击Next即可.</p><h4 id="3-测试"><a href="#3-测试" class="headerlink" title="3.测试"></a>3.测试</h4><p>​        打开Git Bash，输入node -v查看版本</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$node</span> -v</code></pre><h3 id="三-初始化Hexo"><a href="#三-初始化Hexo" class="headerlink" title="三. 初始化Hexo"></a>三. 初始化Hexo</h3><p>​    在Git Bash中执行命令</p><ul><li><p>安装淘宝镜像源</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> -g cnpm --registry<span class="token operator">=</span>https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre><ul><li>查看cnpm版本</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$cnpm</span> -v</code></pre></li><li><p>安装Hexo</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$cnpm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> -g hexo-cli</code></pre><ul><li>查看Hexo版本</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$hexo</span> -v</code></pre></li><li><p>新建blog文件夹，在文件夹中使用Git Bash</p><h6 id="-1"><a href="#-1" class="headerlink" title></a><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818121220884.png" alt="image-20200818121220884"></h6></li><li><p>初始化Hexo</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$hexo</span> init</code></pre><ul><li>初始化成功提示信息</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">INFO  Cloning hexo-starter https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-starter.gitINFO  Install dependenciesadded 183 packages from 420 contributors and audited 189 packages <span class="token keyword">in</span> 21.577s8 packages are looking <span class="token keyword">for</span> funding  run <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">npm</span> fund<span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token keyword">for</span> detailsfound 0 vulnerabilitiesINFO  Start blogging with Hexo<span class="token operator">!</span></code></pre></li><li><p>开启Hexo</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$hexo</span> s<span class="token variable">$hexo</span> server</code></pre><p>localhost:4000访问</p></li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818122040040.png" alt="image-20200818122040040"></p><h3 id="四-部署Hexo到GitHub"><a href="#四-部署Hexo到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="四. 部署Hexo到GitHub"></a>四. 部署Hexo到GitHub</h3><p>​        在blog文件夹下使用Git Bash</p><ul><li>安装hexo部署插件</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$cnpm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save hexo-deployer-git</code></pre><ul><li><p>在GitHub中创建Repository</p><ul><li>选择New repository</li></ul><h6 id="-2"><a href="#-2" class="headerlink" title></a><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818130526011.png" alt="image-20200818130526011"></h6><ul><li>Repository name:  GitHub用户名.github.io</li><li>Description: 可选</li><li>点击Create repository</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818130814276.png" alt="image-20200818130814276"></p><ul><li>拷贝SSH</li></ul></li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818130859522.png" alt="image-20200818130859522"></p><ul><li><p>配置部署</p><p>在blog根目录的_config.yml中配置如下信息</p><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml">deploy:  type: git  repo: [新建仓库的SSH]  branch: master</code></pre></li><li><p>部署</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token variable">$hexo</span> d<span class="token variable">$hexo</span> deploy</code></pre></li><li><p>测试</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/hexo-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke/image-20200818131553976.png" alt="image-20200818131553976"></p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
